UsersChoiceEvent - Class in view

Constructor to create an event based on the user's choice
UsersChoiceEvent(String, String, String) - Constructor for class view.UsersChoiceEvent
Constructor to create an event based on the user's choice, chose ID of the task and the title of the task
UsersChoiceEvent(String, Date, String, String) - Constructor for class view.UsersChoiceEvent
Constructor to create an event based on the user's choice, the title of the task, the due date of the task and the name of the project of the task
UsersChoiceListener - Interface in view
Interface that needs to be implemented by every class that would serve as a controller between the View and the ListOfTasks
